EnemieslistM4 - a set of sendmail m4 files that implement various antispam
techniques, most notably allowing for scoring or rejection of messages based
on the HELO/EHLO argument and PTR name classifications in the Enemieslist
project via DNSBL-style queries in realtime. For installation questions, see
INSTALL. For support with configuration, email support@enemieslist.com.

http://enemieslist.com/

